1. *Lekar* je pregledao pacijenta i dao mu terapiju. (The doctor examined the patient and gave him therapy.)
2. *Lekara* smo zamolili da nam pomogne. (We asked the doctor to help us.)
3. *Lekaru* je trebalo malo vremena da dijagnostifikuje bolest. (The doctor needed a little time to diagnos the illness.)
4. *Lekare* je u bolnici bilo malo. (There were few doctors in the hospital.)
5. Naš *lekar* nam je rekao da vodimo računa o zdravlju. (Our doctor told us to take care of our health.)
6. *Lekaru* smo platile za njegove usluge. (We paid the doctor for his services.)